nodes.text: An individual was a male Mandalorian warrior who fought on Darvannis with other Mandalorian clans during the war against Zakuul. However, he lost a leg in battle, thus forcing him get a cybernetic replacement. He was later seen talking to another Mandalorian about how it was working for him thus far.

After the war against the Empire was over and the Mandalorians became full members of the Eternal Alliance, he and his fellow Mandalorian were once again working alongside each other on Onderon. They were present at the city of Iziz when they saw Mandalore the Avenger giving the task of hunting down the Ash'ad to the Alliance Commander.
